<p><b>Age Group:</b></p>

<p>The age group filter allows you to limit your search results
to one of four age groups general interest, children, pre-teen, and adult.</p>

<p><b>Literary Form:</b></p>

<p>The literary form filter allows you to limit your search
results to the available literary form based on your search term.</p>

<p><b>Subject:</b></p>

<p>The subject filter allows you to limit your search results
to the available subject form based on your search term.</p>

<p><b>Author:</b></p>

<p>The Author filter allows you to limit your search results to
an author available based on your search term.</p>

<p><b>Language:</b></p>

<p>The Language filter allows you to limit your search results
to the available language based on your search term.</p>

<p><b>What kinds of filters
are available for me?</b></p>

<p><b>Retain filters: </b></p>

<p>The Retain filter checkbox under the search bar allows you
to keep the same facets selected while performing another search.</p>  

<p><b>Limit to available:</b></p>

<p>The limit to available checkbox under the search bar is a
filter to limit the search results to only items that are currently available. </p>